INTENT: Research vector database options for a semantic search feature in a SaaS product

WHY: Architecture decision needed before Q2 sprint planning

FOR: Technical lead and engineering team

CONTEXT:
  domain: vector databases, semantic search, embeddings
  scale: ~1M documents, 1536-dim vectors
  stack: Node.js backend, AWS deployment
  budget: prefer open-source or low-cost managed

CONSTRAINTS:
  format: comparison table + recommendation
  length: < 500 words
  tone: technical, concise

DECOMPOSE:
  task-1: Survey top options (Pinecone, Weaviate, Qdrant, pgvector, Chroma)
  task-2: Compare on: cost, latency, managed vs self-hosted, SDK support
  task-3: Recommend best fit with rationale
  strategy: sequential
